{"tid":1921933,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王喜拍《頭條》少後顧之憂","createTime":"2020-03-12T09:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T09:17:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"346b69df6c62f80f11e880f341e347c8e5654522","tid":1921933,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:10:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200312/C7D3OCDEOGUTSCEOP5JEUTFWQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200312%2FC7D3OCDEOGUTSCEOP5JEUTFWQI%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=18f7593b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200312%2FC7D3OCDEOGUTSCEOP5JEUTFWQI%2F&h=4ce60ae5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200312/C7D3OCDEOGUTSCEOP5JEUTFWQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n王喜拍《頭條》少後顧之憂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200312/large/1583933535_4926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200312%2Flarge%2F1583933535_4926.jpg&h=c0d7f463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王喜昨日為港台節目開工，笑說要將場口保密給觀眾驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n王喜參與港台節目《頭條新聞》中的「驚方訊息」，得到市民的共鳴，卻觸動警務處處長鄧炳強的神經。不過王喜昨日現身廣播道再為節目拍外景，他笑言為讓觀眾有驚喜，不透露拍攝場口。雖然收到投訴，但沒有收到上頭壓力，王喜還叫觀眾不用擔心：「反而少了後顧之憂，按照監製指示，方向冇乜大分別，手法同切入點冇乜改變，大家更努力、更賣力，希望唔好辜負對呢個節目有期望觀眾。」<br />\n<br />\n面對社會上每日發生的事，王喜稱會以有幽默手法、嬉笑怒罵反映社會：「鄧生已示範了佢哋能夠被幽默、佢哋系統入面幽默嗰條線，個門檻，都好幽默，哈哈。喺主題之下將社會唔同事件集合成編，然後用鄧生嗰一種幽默程度同門檻去tailor made一啲幽默又客氣說話去表達我哋節目。」至於會否擔心被停播，他表示不是由他考慮，又深信節目質素高及受歡迎，正常電視台營運者會搶着播。<br />\n<br />\n採訪、攝影：王連連"},{"pid":"15eebfdc13f268dfbebb5c2bcf50704bb5f7455d","tid":1921933,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"Rthk唔係好大壓力咩 森哥都講到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}